.  No male made such a response in the  current periods but a small proportion of females did.  The contrast brings out the difference between doing something for fun and doing it as a necessity.  To many women, 
entering into commercial sexual relationships is a matter of survival and there will always be a small proportion of them regardless of the consequences
.  The small size of such a group is compensated for by the number of sexual partners.  The general picture portrayed by Table 11 has serious implications for the spread of AIDS.\par 
